<section class="faq-section section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="kicker" style="justify-content:center;" data-en="Common Questions" data-ar="الأسئلة الشائعة">Common Questions</div>
      <h2 class="h2" data-en="Answers to the<br><em>Questions We Hear Most.</em>" data-ar="إجابات على<br><em>الأسئلة الأكثر شيوعاً.</em>">Answers to the<br><em>Questions We Hear Most.</em></h2>
      <div class="h2-rule" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--b0),transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-cols reveal">
      <div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="What exactly is IRAS® and how is it different from existing school management software?" data-ar="ما هو إيراس® بالضبط وكيف يختلف عن برامج إدارة المدارس الموجودة؟">What exactly is IRAS® and how is it different from existing school management software?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="IRAS® (Intelligent Recognition and Analytics System) is an AI-powered school intelligence platform built on IoT hardware — wearable devices, gateway servers, and real-time monitoring infrastructure. Unlike traditional software, IRAS® operates at the physical level: it knows when a student enters the campus, identifies anomalies, and notifies parents and administrators automatically, without manual data entry from staff." data-ar="إيراس® منصة ذكاء مدرسي مدعومة بالذكاء الاصطناعي مبنية على أجهزة إنترنت الأشياء. على عكس البرامج التقليدية، يعمل إيراس® على المستوى المادي: يعرف متى يدخل الطالب الحرم ويُعرِّف الحالات الشاذة ويُخطر أولياء الأمور والإداريين تلقائياً.">IRAS® is an AI-powered school intelligence platform built on IoT hardware — wearable devices, gateway servers, and real-time monitoring infrastructure. Unlike traditional software, IRAS® operates at the physical level: it knows when a student enters the campus, identifies anomalies, and notifies parents and administrators automatically, without manual data entry.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="Is IRAS® proven or is this pre-launch technology?" data-ar="هل إيراس® تقنية مُثبَتة أم أنها تقنية ما قبل الإطلاق؟">Is IRAS® proven or is this pre-launch technology?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="IRAS® is operationally deployed across 22 schools in the UAE and active in Qatar. Neuronso Technology spent four years building and testing the platform before its 2025 launch. Egypt is not a pilot — it is the next franchise territory for a platform with a live operational track record." data-ar="إيراس® مُنشَر تشغيلياً في 22 مدرسة في الإمارات وفعّال في قطر. أمضت نيورونسو تكنولوجي أربع سنوات في بناء المنصة واختبارها قبل إطلاقها عام 2025.">IRAS® is operationally deployed across 22 schools in the UAE and active in Qatar. Neuronso Technology spent four years building and testing the platform before its 2025 launch. Egypt is not a pilot — it is the next franchise territory for a platform with a live operational track record.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="How is student data protected?" data-ar="كيف تُحمى بيانات الطلاب؟">How is student data protected?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="All student data is encrypted in transit and at rest. Access is role-based — parents see only their child's data, administrators see school-level data. IRAS® deployments in Egypt are structured to comply with Egyptian Personal Data Protection Law No. 151 of 2020. No student data is sold or shared with third parties." data-ar="جميع بيانات الطلاب مُشفَّرة أثناء النقل والتخزين. الوصول مستند إلى الأدوار — يرى أولياء الأمور فقط بيانات طفلهم.">All student data is encrypted in transit and at rest. Access is role-based. IRAS® deployments in Egypt are structured to comply with Egyptian Personal Data Protection Law No. 151 of 2020. No student data is sold or shared with third parties.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="Who is Neuronso Technology and what is their relationship with Blu9L?" data-ar="من هي نيورونسو تكنولوجي وما علاقتها ببلو9إل؟">Who is Neuronso Technology and what is their relationship with Blu9L?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="Neuronso Technology for Artificial Intelligence Applications &amp; Services L.L.C is the developer and owner of the IRAS® platform. Registered in Dubai Silicon Oasis (License 1115725), Neuronso is led by CEO Naim Messai. Blu9L holds the exclusive IRAS® franchise rights for the Arab Republic of Egypt under a formal franchise agreement — the only company authorised to deploy IRAS® across Egypt." data-ar="نيورونسو تكنولوجي هي المطوّر والمالك لمنصة إيراس®، مسجّلة في دبي سيليكون أوسيس بموجب الرخصة 1115725. تمتلك بلو9إل حقوق امتياز إيراس® الحصرية لجمهورية مصر العربية.">Neuronso Technology for AI Applications &amp; Services L.L.C is the developer and owner of the IRAS® platform, registered in Dubai Silicon Oasis (License 1115725), led by CEO Naim Messai. Blu9L holds the exclusive IRAS® franchise rights for Egypt — the only company authorised to deploy IRAS® across the country.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="How long does a typical school deployment take?" data-ar="كم يستغرق نشر مدرسة نموذجية؟">How long does a typical school deployment take?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="A full school deployment — from initial assessment through to live operations — typically takes four to eight weeks depending on campus size and complexity. The process includes hardware installation, network configuration, platform setup, and comprehensive staff and parent training. Schools experience no disruption to daily operations during installation." data-ar="يستغرق نشر المدرسة الكامل — من التقييم الأولي حتى العمليات الحية — عادةً من أربعة إلى ثمانية أسابيع.">A full deployment — from initial assessment to live operations — typically takes four to eight weeks depending on campus size. The process includes hardware installation, network configuration, platform setup, and comprehensive staff training. No disruption to daily operations during installation.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-q" data-en="Is IRAS® suitable for our school size and type?" data-ar="هل إيراس® مناسب لحجم ونوع مدرستنا؟">Is IRAS® suitable for our school size and type?</div>
          <div class="faq-a" data-en="IRAS® is designed for private schools across multiple scale categories — from schools with a few hundred students to campuses with several thousand. Neuronso Technology offers tiered service packages matched to each school's operational profile and annual fee structure. Blu9L's team will assess your specific requirements during an initial consultation." data-ar="صُمِّم إيراس® للمدارس الخاصة عبر فئات حجم متعددة. تقدّم نيورونسو تكنولوجي حزم خدمات متدرجة تتناسب مع الملف التشغيلي لكل مدرسة.">IRAS® is designed for private schools across multiple scale categories. Neuronso Technology offers tiered service packages matched to each school's operational profile. Blu9L's team will assess your specific requirements during an initial consultation.</div>
        </div>
